title: The Fortune Cookie (Jack Lemmon - Walter Matthau 1966)
description:
This torrent was originally uploaded by Crash247 over at Demonoid. 

The film is "a classic" and needs to be further disseminated, so I "stole it" to make it more widely available. 

Decent movie, give it shot, better than 75% of the crap out today.


                      The Fortune Cookie (1966)


A cameraman gets injured by a football player during a game and goes to the hospital. There, his cunning brother in law (who happens to be a lawyer) convinces him to pretend that his legs have been paralyzed. This way, they can receive a huge indemnity from the insurance company. Of course, the insurance company's men suspect that the paralysis is a fake one, and so a big "game" begins. The first collaboration of the successful team of Walter Matthau and Jack Lemmon.
